graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js >= 22.0.0]
    Dashboard -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.24+]
    Dashboard -->|platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+]
    Dashboard -->|auth proxy| KubeRBAC[kube-rbac-proxy]
    Dashboard -.->|metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus 2.x]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|watches| ODHOp[ODH/RHOAI Operator<br/>DataScienceCluster]
    Dashboard -->|manages| Notebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks<br/>Notebook CR]
    Dashboard -->|watches| KServe[KServe<br/>InferenceService CR]
    Dashboard -->|manages| ModelReg[Model Registry Operator<br/>ModelRegistry CR]
    Dashboard -->|watches| TrustyAI[TrustyAI<br/>GuardrailsOrchestrator CR]
    Dashboard -->|watches| Feast[Feast<br/>FeatureStore CR]
    Dashboard -->|watches| LlamaStack[LlamaStack<br/>LlamaStackDistribution CR]
    Dashboard -.->|certs| CertManager[cert-manager]

    %% Integration Points
    DataScientist[Data Scientists] -->|UI access| Dashboard
    Admins[Administrators] -->|configure| Dashboard

    %% External Services
    Dashboard -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    Dashboard -.->|proxy| PromSvc[Prometheus Service<br/>9091/TCP HTTP]
    Dashboard -.->|proxy| ModelRegSvc[Model Registry Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP]

    %% Feature Packages
    subgraph "Feature Packages (Plugins)"
        GenAI[Gen AI Module]
        ModelRegPlugin[Model Registry Module]
        MLflow[MLflow Module]
        AutoML[AutoML Module]
        AutoRAG[AutoRAG Module]
        KServePlugin[KServe Module]
    end

    Dashboard -.->|uses| GenAI
    Dashboard -.->|uses| ModelRegPlugin
    Dashboard -.->|uses| MLflow
    Dashboard -.->|uses| AutoML
    Dashboard -.->|uses| AutoRAG
    Dashboard -.->|uses| KServePlugin

